          "slidecontent": "• Ransomware can halt entire logistics networks within minutes, not just individual machines\n\n• AI-dependent systems multiply the damage\n\n• A single compromised entry point (such as a supplier portal) can cascade across your whole operation\n\n• Offline backups and tested recovery plans are non-negotiable\n\n• Staff awareness is your first line of defence against phishing and social engineering attacks\n\n• Start small: review your incident response plan this week and identify one gap to address"
